text: Thanks guy. Rough day out there. I was keeping a 3:35 pace until about mile 20 and then a hip flexor injury I've been dealing with for the past month flared up. I ended up finishing in 3:47 which isn't terrible but I had felt like a 3:30 was possible at like mile 18 so I'm mildly bummed.
That’s amazing in this horrible weather!!
